      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="15693388">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45449329/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u45449329-4.jpg" alt="wit" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15693388/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15693388/" class="">第83页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45449329/" class=" " title="wit">wit</a>
                (Quem librum legis?)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="15693388">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">当今世界上共有12个国家拥有航空母舰，其中美国拥有世界上最多和最大的航空母舰。其他11个国家的全部航母加起来，从质量和性能上说，也不及美国航空母舰实力的1/10.</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-12-06 15:58</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
